entry.title: amir-kedis/Assembly-x86-helper
entry.summary: Assembly x86 Helper repository, a collaborative initiative by students from Cairo University's Faculty of Engineering CMP26 to make a comprehensive resource hub for teams and individuals delving into the world of low-level x86 programming, with a specific focus on game development.
